00:01:03,845 --> 00:01:09,859
=The Empress Dowager On A Second Spring=

21
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:13,696
Though Xiao Hu isn't the Regent's,

22
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,936
he's not yours either.

23
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:19,959
You... you...

24
00:01:23,552 --> 00:01:25,344
There's another man?

25
00:01:25,888 --> 00:01:26,464
You...

26
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:29,959
(Let's see how you'll react.)

27
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:40,959
I've decided.

28
00:01:41,959 --> 00:01:42,976
No matter who you have

29
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,704
or who Xiao Hu's father is,

30
00:01:44,704 --> 00:01:45,280
I will

31
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,959
treat him as my own.

32
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,144
I know.

33
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:02,159
But this time,

34
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:04,920
you truly can't treat him as your own.

35
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,672
Because he is His Majesty's son.

36
00:02:15,936 --> 00:02:18,688
Swallow that thought right now.

37
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,952
I'm not his mother.

38
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,256
You are not?

39
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,520
Of course not.

40
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:31,840
You are not. Cuizhu is not.

41
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:32,840
Then who is?

42
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,120
Is there someone else?

43
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,599
My maid Rong gave birth to him.

44
00:02:47,223 --> 00:02:51,136
=Episode 18=

45
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,216
Where is the palace?

46
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,800
