47
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,896
I go wherever I wish.

48
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,650
So this is

49
00:03:16,512 --> 00:03:18,208
what it feels like to live

50
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,000
an ordinary life with you.

51
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,400
I won't let you marry Zhao Chengtian.

52
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,319
I want him dead.

53
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,560
What do you mean?

54
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,728
Xiao Hu is in his grasp now.

55
00:03:42,272 --> 00:03:43,264
We've endured him enough.

56
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,599
It's time to end this.

57
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,879
How do we end it?

58
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,639
Lure him into rebellion,

59
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,000
bringing his own doom.

60
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,240
But won't

61
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:02,360
the plan's risk be too great?

62
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,320
Can't we just eliminate him

63
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,599
physically?

64
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,639
He'd be seen as a victim.

65
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,439
His crimes

66
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,840
couldn't be exposed to the world.

67
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,479
Even His Majesty

68
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,160
would bear the charge
of murdering his uncle.

69
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,240
It's too merciful for him.

70
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,808
I understand.

71
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,399
He can't die easily.

72
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,959
He must be condemned for eternity.

73
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,040
But

74
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:32,079
I don't want you risking yourself.

75
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,480
You nearly died for me.

76
00:04:38,176 --> 00:04:39,399
A little risk is nothing.

77
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:41,480
Tell me.

78
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,279
What do you need me to do?

79
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:53,040
To stage a performance.

80
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,488
As long as I can be with you

81
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:02,240
and Xiao Hu grows up healthy,

82
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:03,800
I'll do anything.

83
00:05:15,581 --> 00:05:18,016
(Xuanming Palace)

84
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,639
Your Majesty.

85
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:22,688
Calm your anger.

86
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:25,360
What more is there to say?

87
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:27,399
You've been utterly bewitched by her.

88
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:28,360
You're on her side now.

89
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,199
An Empress Dowager remarrying?

90
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,560
A huge laughingstock.

91
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,319
How dare you speak of it?

92
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,000
Not just remarrying.

93
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,920
You'd honor him as Emperor Emeritus?

94
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,160
Your family of three

95
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,920
is taking my entire empire.

96
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,480
For causing Your Majesty anguish,

97
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,240
I deserve death ten thousand times.

98
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,560
Your Majesty, calm yourself.

99
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:50,496
Hear me out.

100
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,759
What's left to say?

101
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,639
Xiao Hu is not the Regent's child.

102
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:58,519
You went to the Regent's Manor
for a blood test,

103
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,800
and now you lie to me?

104
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,664
Do you think I'd believe...

105
00:06:01,664 --> 00:06:03,360
The blood paternity test was faked.

106
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,199
Your Majesty,

107
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:05,680
I can prove

108
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,120
the blood test was Her Majesty's ploy

109
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,040
to free me.

110
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,600
Master,

111
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,120
how can you still trust her?

112
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,360
This woman even faked a blood test.

113
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,839
What else can be real?

114
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,744
This

115
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:28,240
is ironclad proof
that Xiao Hu is Your Majesty's son.

116
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,384
Does Your Majesty recall

117
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,120
being drunk two years ago

118
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,184
and storming my palace at night?

119
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:40,839
Empress Dowager.

120
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,240
How could you...

121
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:46,048
How could you do such a thing?

122
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,952
You actually... with my uncle?

123
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:54,000
How am I supposed to face the world now?

124
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,959
Escort His Majesty
to the side hall to rest.

125
00:07:00,032 --> 00:07:01,040
Take good care of him.

126
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,040
Yes, Your Majesty.

127
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:12,639
Your Majesty.

128
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,720
Your Majesty.

129
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,199
What?

130
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,839
Xiao Hu is my son?

131
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,360
Since you took the throne,

132
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,879
