133
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,000
Many children in the palace
died by his hands.

134
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,040
We kept it secret from you

135
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,839
to deceive the Regent as well

136
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,440
and preserve

137
00:07:34,112 --> 00:07:35,519
a bloodline for you.

138
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,984
So I agreed to marry the Regent

139
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,224
to buy us crucial time

140
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,208
to ultimately overthrow him.

141
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,639
But why should I believe you?

142
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,399
By now,

143
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,584
do you still believe

144
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,432
I murdered your mother?

145
00:07:55,104 --> 00:07:55,744
Isn't it true?

146
00:07:55,936 --> 00:07:56,800
No.

147
00:08:04,416 --> 00:08:05,000
Mr. Cheng,

148
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,480
following your clues,

149
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,560
we found the late Empress's
personal maid.

150
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:12,040
She gave me her mistress's letter
to Her Majesty.

151
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,920
The late Empress
was watched by the Regent.

152
00:08:22,368 --> 00:08:23,519
She secretly told her maid

153
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,879
to deliver this letter.

154
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,920
Give this letter

155
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,920
to Rong before you leave.

156
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,399
Tell her

157
00:08:30,752 --> 00:08:31,360
His Majesty

158
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,864
(Late Empress)

159
00:08:32,864 --> 00:08:34,112
is entrusted to her care now.

160
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,720
Yes.

161
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,000
(After she passed,)

162
00:08:44,512 --> 00:08:46,432
(the Regent spread rumors
of their discord.)

163
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,480
- (The maid wouldn't lie)
- Pleas stop.

164
00:08:48,832 --> 00:08:49,568
(or dare fight.)

165
00:08:49,568 --> 00:08:51,000
Rong, listen to me.

166
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:54,159
(Eventually, she fled
to her hometown with the letter.)

167
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,328
Due to the Regent,

168
00:09:00,032 --> 00:09:01,952
Her Majesty couldn't see
the late Empress

169
00:09:01,952 --> 00:09:03,039
and has regretted it.

170
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,799
After the late Emperor died,

171
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:07,679
to placate the Regent

172
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,200
and keep the throne,

173
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,879
(Her Majesty yielded to him.)

174
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,360
(Later, she tarnished
her own name to protect)

175
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,320
(your heir)

176
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:20,480
(and forbade us from telling anyone.)

177
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:29,440
Today I defy Her Majesty's decree

178
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:30,399
because I can't

179
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:32,879
bear watching her
suffer slander and betrayal.

180
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:34,799
I await punishment.

181
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,696
How could I be so blind?

182
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:40,720
I've let you endure such injustice.

183
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,480
I beg forgiveness.

184
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,200
Empress Dowager...

185
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:57,039
Mother,

186
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:00,000
punish your unworthy son.

187
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,679
Let the past

188
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,159
be forgotten.

189
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,000
Since

190
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,759
I promised the late Empress,

191
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:20,992
I shall

192
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,336
