193
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,759
Your Majesty's throne.

194
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,120
Instead of skimming the surface,

195
00:10:27,424 --> 00:10:28,576
we'll strike at the root.

196
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,600
Her Majesty and I have devised a plan,

197
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,960
