198
00:10:35,552 --> 00:10:36,640
I will help.

199
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:44,759
You fool.

200
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,960
The late Empress's maid...

201
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,320
