216
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,639
To dispel celestial omens

217
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:35,039
and pray for national prosperity,

218
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,736
I hereby approve

219
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:39,808
Empress Dowager Zhaohui's marriage
to the Regent

220
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,000
